Company Profile:
In search of … .Great Minds
World Scientific Publishing since its inception in 1981, the Group has grown to establish itself as one of the world’s leading academics publishers and the largest in the Asia-Pacific. With its headquarters in Singapore and offices in New Jersey, London, Hong Kong, Taipei, Beijing, Shanghai and Chennai, it now publishes about 500 titles a year and 120 journals in various fields. Prestigious universities, such as Caltech, Cambridge, Cornell, Harvard, MIT, Oxford, Princeton, Stanford and Yale have adopted many of our titles as textbooks. WSPC have also published many Nobel- Laureate authors’ book. The Company is searching for talented, innovative and result oriented individual to join our dynamic team in our HQ in Singapore:
Job Description:Responsibilities:Perform quality check of book chapters, journal articles and journal references
Creating and uploading content onto website and checking of third party websites
Requirements:Organized, meticulous and able to prioritise
On the job training will be provided
A level graduates/ Students waiting for results/ ORD Personnel/ Undergraduates are welcome to apply
Interested candidates are invited to send in your detailed resume and include expected remuneration, availablility period to hr@wspc.com.sg
